  "status": "Stagnant",
  "summary": "This EIP extends any other token standard to provide: * Explicit rights for the token holder related to commercial exploitation, derivative works, and reproduction; * [EIP-5218](./eip-5218.md) interface for creating, viewing, and checking the status of licenses * Standard format for extended license information in the token metadata; * Standard events to track off chain creation of derivative works, commercial exploitation, and reproduction; * On chain tracking of derivative works and reproductions * Additional required fields in the smart contract to reference the copyright owner * Function calls for commercial exploitation, derivative works and reproduction.",
  "title": "NFT Legal Use, Repurposing, and Remixing"
